{
  "stem": "1413.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I, for one was told that his German doctors about his condition, and I was the first one was told by the German who was in charge there, that he died.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked the name up last night again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I owe you that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It might be F-E-L-D-D-A-F-I-N-G I'll have to look it up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was no camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was out in the fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Open fields.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we searched to get back to the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was not easy because first of all, I stole a bicycle [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] to search for food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, yeah-- I skipped a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a whole lot I skipped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were three of us who said, one for one, and all for each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was trying to  get some food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of us couldn't walk, and that bicycle-- and we went from town to town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The one who couldn't  walk was sitting on the bike and we were holding the bike with him on top.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now the same two guys-- I'm going to tell you something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We walked for  two weeks-- I told you before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You might say I jump-- but I want everything out there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I want the world to know-- the future-- what's happened to me, and to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The three of us said, if there is one piece of bread, we're going to share the three.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The first one went into a house and stole a loaf of bread off the table.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Desperate.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Desperate.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Shared it with three.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My turn.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went into a house-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] wooden shoes-- not wooden shoes from Holland, but what we got up in the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No socks.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
